# Corvax N14
job-name-caesar-legion-centurion = Centurion
job-description-caesar-legion-centurion = The most trusted commanders of Caesar's Legion - the Centurions. These hardened frontline officers wear armor composed of parts scavenged from fallen enemies.
job-name-caesar-legion-venator = Venator
job-description-caesar-legion-venator = There are no clear boundaries for them. They operate deep behind enemy lines for extended periods, mimicking enemy customs, yet this does not taint them.
job-name-caesar-legion-dean = Dean
job-description-caesar-legion-dean = Junior commander of the Legion.
job-name-caesar-legion-legionnaire-veteran = Legion Veteran
job-description-caesar-legionnaire-veteran = Take an ordinary legionnaire and age him ten years. His health may not improve, but the experience gained more than compensates for it. People don't live long in the Legion.
job-name-caesar-legion-legionnaire-warrior = Legion Warrior
job-description-caesar-legionnaire-warrior = A trained warrior of the Legion.
job-name-caesar-legion-legionnaire-recruit = Legion Recruit
job-description-caesar-legionnaire-recruit = A new recruit of the Legion.
job-name-caesar-legion-slave = Caesar's Legion Slave
job-description-caesar-legion-slave = You are a slave, you are obligated to serve Caesar's Legion, your life is in their hands.

# Western BoS
job-name-bos-west-elder-comm = Western Brotherhood Elder Commander
job-description-bos-west-elder-comm = The leader of the Western Brotherhood of Steel chapter, possessing the experience and knowledge to manage the organization.
job-name-bos-west-paladin = Western Brotherhood Paladin
job-description-bos-west-paladin = An elite soldier of the Western Brotherhood of Steel, trained in the use of power armor.
job-name-bos-west-knight = Western Brotherhood Knight
job-description-bos-west-knight = An experienced warrior of the Western Brotherhood of Steel, protecting its interests and technologies.
job-name-bos-west-scribe = Western Brotherhood Scribe
job-description-bos-west-scribe = A keeper of knowledge and technology for the Western Brotherhood of Steel, engaged in research and documentation.
job-name-bos-west-gunsmith = Western Brotherhood Gunsmith
job-description-bos-west-gunsmith = A novice in the Western Brotherhood of Steel just beginning their journey. Performs basic weapon and equipment repair and maintenance operations while trying not to make mistakes.
